    "name": "Undercover Fools",
    "steam_appid": 3249560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/f4f9e661af4413b6537012ecb8e1748a.avif?t=1749153371\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras_big/f4f9e661af4413b6537012ecb8e1748a.avif?t=1749153371 width=800 height=251 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Undercover Fools</i></strong>是一款关于间谍的合作动作游戏，集结团队或单独行动潜入受保护的建筑物，避开危险的陷阱并执行任务配备最酷的间谍装备，执行具有挑战性的任务！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行精通</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/8dd3a5fd5331bc101113eb16ec05f93c.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/8dd3a5fd5331bc101113eb16ec05f93c.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/8dd3a5fd5331bc101113eb16ec05f93c.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的主要目标是不被发现。利用阴影和僻静的地方来避免被守卫发现，或者用特殊的小工具分散敌人的注意力。你采取的每一步都可以是决定性的 - 谨慎行事！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每次 - 一个新的任务</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/04c31d59810c1a4f8c40d020bef840a4.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/04c31d59810c1a4f8c40d020bef840a4.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/04c31d59810c1a4f8c40d020bef840a4.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序地图生成确保你每次进入时房间、障碍物和敌人的独特布局。这使得每次尝试都变得不可预测，并为您的间谍冒险增添惊喜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>间谍小工具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/d2f141ae7bfb428e66ed15624a932920.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/d2f141ae7bfb428e66ed15624a932920.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/d2f141ae7bfb428e66ed15624a932920.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的装备是成功的关键。你拥有强大的间谍工具可供使用：抓钩、干扰器、麻醉枪等等。每个小工具都有助于绕过障碍或给安全带来困难。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种威胁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/f0cb909ca6c48078b76b1554339a84bf.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/f0cb909ca6c48078b76b1554339a84bf.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/f0cb909ca6c48078b76b1554339a84bf.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从巡逻警卫到监控摄像头和快速无人机。每种类型的保护都需要特殊的方法。运用敏捷和智慧来消除或避免危险。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择路径</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/e4892e6ce8875061223a6aebbf1d4daa.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/e4892e6ce8875061223a6aebbf1d4daa.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/e4892e6ce8875061223a6aebbf1d4daa.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解后门，烧穿屋顶上的锁，或从正门进入。您的成功取决于策略的选择。使用不同的方法来实现你的目标 - 从隐蔽渗透到牵制机动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>休闲娱乐区</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/12eed2dd7f9615fda78f1ec90e97eb90.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/12eed2dd7f9615fda78f1ec90e97eb90.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/12eed2dd7f9615fda78f1ec90e97eb90.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧张的任务结束后，在大厅放松一下！在令人兴奋的迷你游戏中测试自己：台球、保龄球、篮球、篮球或其他活跃的游戏。如果您想放松一下，可以去酒吧与朋友聊天并为下一个任务做好准备。大厅是您放松和计划的中心！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完美间谍</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/4c26d84729968d463b8e9d1b72d2c7e0.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/4c26d84729968d463b8e9d1b72d2c7e0.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/4c26d84729968d463b8e9d1b72d2c7e0.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级您的技能以提高任务的效率。提高你的隐秘性、速度、黑客攻击或使用小工具的能力。每个新级别都会为完成任务提供新的机会。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>非常时尚</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/82ae3f4f0a5faae208eb3f649f8d0901.poster.avif?t=1749153371\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/82ae3f4f0a5faae208eb3f649f8d0901.webm?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249560/extras/82ae3f4f0a5faae208eb3f649f8d0901.mp4?t=1749153371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建一个独特的间谍！用各种服装和配饰改变你的造型。使用情绪和手势来表达自己 - 从厚颜无耻的眨眼到“全部清除”信号。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >事情可能会出错：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong><i>Undercover Fools</i></strong>中，失败也是乐趣的一部分！您的团队可能会意外吸引警卫、引发警报，甚至破坏整个计划。然而，你总能凭借智慧、快速行动和一点运气逃脱困境。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >添加到<strong>愿望清单</strong>并敬请关注！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
